@startuml Sequence_Admin_MonitoringAnalytics
title Quản Trị - Giám Sát & Phân Tích

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant AnalyticsService as "Analytics\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Dashboard Thống Kê ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Thống kê"
FrontEnd -> AnalyticsService: GET /api/admin/dashboard
AnalyticsService -> Database: Query statistics
Database --> AnalyticsService: Stats data
AnalyticsService --> FrontEnd: Dashboard data
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị dashboard\n(tổng users, companies, jobs)

== Thống Kê Người Dùng ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Người dùng"
FrontEnd -> AnalyticsService: GET /api/admin/analytics/users
AnalyticsService -> Database: Query user growth
Database --> AnalyticsService: User stats
AnalyticsService --> FrontEnd: User data
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị biểu đồ tăng trưởng

== Thống Kê Công Ty ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Công ty"
FrontEnd -> AnalyticsService: GET /api/admin/analytics/companies
AnalyticsService -> Database: Query company stats
Database --> AnalyticsService: Company data
AnalyticsService --> FrontEnd: Data
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị thống kê công ty

== Thống Kê Công Việc ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Công việc"
FrontEnd -> AnalyticsService: GET /api/admin/analytics/jobs
AnalyticsService -> Database: Query job stats
Database --> AnalyticsService: Job data
AnalyticsService --> FrontEnd: Data
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị thống kê công việc

== Thống Kê Ứng Tuyển ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Ứng tuyển"
FrontEnd -> AnalyticsService: GET /api/admin/analytics/applications
AnalyticsService -> Database: Query application stats
Database --> AnalyticsService: Application data
AnalyticsService --> FrontEnd: Data
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị thống kê ứng tuyển

== Xuất Báo Cáo ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Xuất báo cáo"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show export options
Admin -> FrontEnd: Chọn định dạng (Excel/PDF)
FrontEnd -> AnalyticsService: POST /api/admin/analytics/export\n(format)
AnalyticsService -> Database: Get all data
Database --> AnalyticsService: Complete data
AnalyticsService -> AnalyticsService: Generate file
AnalyticsService --> FrontEnd: File URL
FrontEnd --> Admin: Download file

@enduml
